#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.log1p.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.log1p"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:1 of
msgid "Return the natural logarithm of one plus the input tensor, element-wise."
msgstr "返回输入张量加一后的自然对数，逐元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:3 of
msgid "Calculates ``log(1 + x)``."
msgstr "计算 ``log(1 + x)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:5 of
msgid "Input values."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:17 of
msgid "**y** -- Natural logarithm of `1 + x`, element-wise."
msgstr "**y** -- `1 + x` 的自然对数，逐元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`expm1`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:23 of
msgid "``exp(x) - 1``, the inverse of `log1p`."
msgstr "``exp(x) - 1``，是 `log1p` 的反函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:26 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:27 of
msgid ""
"For real-valued input, `log1p` is accurate also for `x` so small that `1 "
"+ x == 1` in floating-point accuracy."
msgstr ""
"对于实数输入，`log1p` 对于非常小的 `x`（小到在浮点精度下 `1 + x == 1`）也"
"是准确的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:30 of
msgid ""
"Logarithm is a multivalued function: for each `x` there is an infinite "
"number of `z` such that `exp(z) = 1 + x`. The convention is to return the"
" `z` whose imaginary part lies in `[-pi, pi]`."
msgstr ""
"对数是一个多值函数：对于每个 `x`，存在无限多个 `z` 使得 `exp(z) = 1 + x`"
"。约定返回虚部位于 `[-pi, pi]` 范围内的 `z`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:34 of
msgid ""
"For real-valued input data types, `log1p` always returns real output. For"
" each value that cannot be expressed as a real number or infinity, it "
"yields ``nan`` and sets the `invalid` floating point error flag."
msgstr ""
"对于实数输入数据类型，`log1p` 总是返回实数输出。对于无法表示为实数或"
"无穷大的值，它返回 ``nan`` 并设置 `invalid` 浮点错误标志。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:38 of
msgid ""
"For complex-valued input, `log1p` is a complex analytical function that "
"has a branch cut `[-inf, -1]` and is continuous from above on it. `log1p`"
" handles the floating-point negative zero as an infinitesimal negative "
"number, conforming to the C99 standard."
msgstr ""
"对于复数输入，`log1p` 是一个复解析函数，它在 `[-inf, -1]` 处有分支切割，"
"并在其上从上方连续。`log1p` 将浮点负零视为无穷小的负数，符合 C99 标准。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:44 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:45 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I.A. Stegun, \"Handbook of Mathematical Functions\", "
"10th printing, 1964, pp. 67. http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"
msgstr ""
"M. Abramowitz 和 I.A. Stegun，《数学函数手册》，第 10 版，1964 年，第 67 "
"页。http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log1p.log1p:47 of
msgid "Wikipedia, \"Logarithm\". http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithm"
msgstr "维基百科，“对数”。http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithm"

